        <h3>Expert Witness Services</h3>
        <p>Dr. Lavian has provided expert witness testimony in patent infringement cases, standards compliance disputes, network architecture patent litigation, and communications system design disputes. His ability to communicate complex technical concepts to judges and juries, combined with his unimpeachable credentials and comprehensive knowledge base, makes him an invaluable asset in technical litigation matters.</p>

        <p>Whether the matter involves fundamental network communications principles, advanced protocol analysis, standards interpretation, or patent validity questions, Dr. Lavian brings decades of professional experience and scientific rigor to his expert opinions. He conducts thorough technical analysis, reviews relevant documentation and prior art, and develops clear, well-reasoned conclusions that withstand rigorous cross-examination.</p>

        <h3>Contact and Additional Information</h3>
        <p>For more information about Dr. Lavian's availability as an expert witness in network communications matters, please contact his office. He is available for consultation, expert opinion development, report writing, and testimony in cases involving telecommunications, network communications technologies, and related fields.</p>

